-- fibonacci-crystal.cell: compute fibonacci, then crystallize
-- The LLM computes fib(10), crystallize writes the вҠў= algorithm

вҠў fib
  given n вүЎ 10
  yield result

  вҲҙ Compute the В«nВ»th Fibonacci number.
    fib(0)=0, fib(1)=1, fib(n)=fib(n-1)+fib(n-2).

  вҠЁ result = 55

вҠў crystallize
  given В§fib
  given fibвҶ’result
  yield В§fib', is-faithful

  вҲҙ Read В«В§fibВ». It computes Fibonacci numbers.
    Write a вҠў= expression using Cell primitives that computes fib(n).
    Return the crystallized cell and faithfulness.

вҠў verify-crystal
  given В§fib'
  given crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful
  given fibвҶ’result
  yield approved

  вҲҙ Does В«В§fib'В» produce 55 for n=10?
    Compare against В«fibвҶ’resultВ».

  вҠЁ if approved and crystallizeвҶ’is-faithful then В§fib' may replace В§fib
